meta {
  name: VOZVRAT (REFUND)
  type: http
  seq: 3
}

post {
  url: {{url}}
  body: json
  auth: inherit
}

body:json {
  {
    "task": "refund",
    "data": {
      "amount": 0.5
      //"tagRRN": "763148028440"
    }
  }
}

settings {
  encodeUrl: true
  timeout: 0
}

docs {
  Cancel the original consumer transaction or return transaction.
  1. If POS did not log in to the Jusan QR server, refund transaction process default
  with the check card process.
  2. If POS has logged in to Jusan QR server, refund request message has filled with
  RRN refund transaction process will with check card process. POS will map one
  unique purchase transaction by RRN. If this purchase has been settle, refund
  request initiates refund transaction, otherwise initiates reversal transaction
  3. POS has logged in, refund request does not have RRN value, POS receive refund
  request will execute refund QR process.
  4.4.1Request
  The task field must fill with value.
  ```
  {
    “task”: “refund”,
    “data”: {
      “amount”: String(Mandatory)
      “tagRRN”: String(got from the RRN of original transactions,length ==12,option)
    “transactionId”: String(got from the transactionId of QR sale, like TR123456, option)
    }
  }
  ```
  PAX Technology 11
  4.4.2Response
  The response message that transacts by card.
  ```
  {
    "data": {
      "cardNo": String, //card PAN,the format example: "100007******8909
      "issuerName": String, //card type
      "tagRRN": String,
      "msg":String,
      "result": int, // 0 indicates success or failure
      "receiptInfo":String,
      “channel”:int //0:other bank card 1:jusan bank card
    }
  }
  ```
  The response message that transacts by scanning the QR code.
  ```
  {
    "data": {
      "msg": String,
      "paymentId": String,
      "result": int,
      "receiptInfo":String,
      “channel”:int //2:jusan QR
    }
  }
  ```
  Example:
  Card：
  ```
  request:
  {
    "task":"refund",
    "data": {
      "tagRRN":"312581054648",
      "amount":"113"
    }
  }
  ```
  ```
  response:
    {
      "data": {
        "cardNo": "555910******0016",
        "channel": 0,
        "issuerName": "MASTER",
        "receiptInfo": "ТОО \"Cullinan\"\nг
        . Алматы, ул. Мака
        т а е в а , 127/1\n И И Н 201240002166\n т е л : +7 777 77
        77\n------------------------------------------------\nCustomer Check 0001\nRRN:
        312581054648\n------------------------------------------------\nRefund 15:04
        05/05/2023\nTerminal ID: 61021804\nCard NO.: 5559********0016\nExpiry:
        12/24\nType: MASTER\nAmount: -113₸\n00:Successfully completed\n",
        "tagRRN": "312581054648",
        "msg": "Operation is Successful",
        "result": 0
      }
    }
  ```
  QR:
  ```
  Request
  PAX Technology 12
  
  {
    "task": "refund",
    "data":{
      "amount": "113"
    }
  }
  ```
  OR
  ```
  {
    "task": "refund",
    "data": {
      "amount":"113",
      ”transactionId”:” TR166490”
    }
  }
  ```
  Response
  ```
  {
    "data": {
      "channel": 2,
      "paymentId": "65268713-8227-43a0-b096-767f80132e5c",
      "msg": "Operation is Successful",
      "result": 0,
      "receiptInfo": "ТОО \"Cullinan\"\nг \
      . Алматы, ул. Макат а е в а , \
      127/1\n И И Н 201240002166\n т е л : +7 777 77 \
  77\n------------------------------------------------\nCustomer Check 0009\nTransaction\
  ID\n------------------------------------------------\nJusan QR Refund 18: 20 \
  28/04/2023\nTerminal ID: 05899991\nAmount: -113₸\n------------------------------------------------\nQR Refund issued\n",
    }
  }
  ```
}
